snippet.title: Oliver and Mom Explore New Countries
snippet.description:
Oliver and Mom explore new countries in this fun learning video. In each episode, they explore a new country, learn about the culture and people, and have lots of fun along the way!

00:00 Oliver and Mom Explore New Countries
07:51 Oliver's journey through different professions
12:36 Learn English Alphabet 
20:31 Learn numbers 1-10 with Diana Roma and Oliver
